summary: I am currently working as a lecturer and researcher at the Department of Modern Languages and Culture at Radboud University. My expertise spans American and European periodical studies, contemporary British fiction and literary criticism and, most prominently, literary Metamodernism and reception studies. I am co-founder of ESPRit: European Society for Periodical Research (https://www.espr-it.eu/) and of the Metamodernism Network (https://ahrc-metamodernism.co.uk/), financed by the British Arts & Humanities Research Council. As of April 2023, I am chair of the expertise groups English Linguistics an English & American Literature and Culture.
